nodes.text: Mundu was a human male who served as a lieutenant in the Resistance during the war between the First Order and the Resistance. He lectured Moxie Freemaker and ordered her to wipe the droid R0-GR's memory before his efforts were interrupted by General Leia Organa.

Mundu first appeared in the LEGO Star Wars: All-Stars third episode "Scouting for Leia/A Mission with Maz" voiced by Danny Jacobs. Despite being referred to as "Lieutenant", Mundu's rank badge indicates he holds the rank of Major.
